{"tid":853973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳宣傳海報遮劉小麗","createTime":"2018-10-09T04:14:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T08:05:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3a4d9b707c2b2f73ef0d771bd0ae54d8c9c9b445","tid":853973,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T04:14:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181009/20517812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181009%2F20517812&d=sZljDrWenY9hBEOu%2BnkSM7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=cfef778b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181009%2F20517812&h=43456d08\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181009/20517812</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月09日 <br />\n<br />\n陳宣傳海報遮劉小麗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181009/large/09la9p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181009%2Flarge%2F09la9p3.jpg&h=32ab719a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網民發現深水埗街市有陳凱欣海報遮擋着劉小麗的海報。Tony Wong fb圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】參加九龍西補選的劉小麗和陳凱欣，近日加快在區內張貼海報宣傳，但有網民發現陳凱欣的競選團隊為了宣傳，不惜將陳凱欣的海報貼在劉小麗的海報上，似刻意想蓋過劉的海報，阻擋對手曝光。本報昨日向陳凱欣負責傳媒的人士查詢，但暫未有回應；而劉小麗希望所有選舉團隊成員「唔好做咁霸道、過份」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民：咁有財力玩小學雞嘢<br />\n<br />\n網民Tony Wong在深水埗街市拍下一張相片，清晰可見陳凱欣的海報遮擋着劉小麗的海報，至少兩張劉的海報被陳的海報覆蓋，不過現場四圍明顯有很多空間位，網民對此也不明所以：「深水埗街市好幾檔，都有劉小麗海報被陳凱欣海報遮住咗。<br />\n<br />\n其實四圍都大把空位，點解都係要咁貼？自己就可鋪天蓋地宣傳，貼晒成個大廈外牆都可以，但係咪人地有限資源去宣傳都唔畀？」<br />\n<br />\n亦有網民批評陳凱欣已坐擁不少財力，為何要這樣宣傳：「咁有財力仲玩呢啲小學雞嘢」、「幅牆咁大，係要蓋住其他人，前政助除咗識幫人打尖，原來海報都要打尖」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，記者亦發現劉小麗的宣傳海報被民建聯區議員的海報遮蓋。<br />\n<br />\n劉小麗回覆《蘋果》查詢時指，由於一個選舉團隊有多人參與，故自己不想針對個別候選人作出批評，只是期望各選舉團隊成員「唔好做咁霸道、過份」，又指今次參選的人數不多，宣傳的空間理應較多，故希望大家也能各自宣傳，勿影響其他參選人的宣傳品。<br />\n<br />\n■記者姚國雄  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n稱人格遭謀殺　馮檢基投訴網台三主持<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【非常人物】抗共牧師郭乃弘　八十歲，我無悔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱人格遭謀殺馮檢基投訴網台三主持<br />\n<br />\n同獲浸大傑出傳理人獎陳凱欣參選轉跑道　師兄勸勿棄求真"},{"pid":"0f4d9c4f11450fbea5af8b0cd67a0d53698fde55","tid":853973,"uid":143499,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T05:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GGzp7LY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGGzp7LY.jpg&h=798bc4c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d03ea45553baaa673472eb50d3c8e7bed7214f9","tid":853973,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"0f4d9c4f11450fbea5af8b0cd67a0d53698fde55","tid":853973,"uid":143499,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T05:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GGzp7LY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGGzp7LY.jpg&h=798bc4c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T05:51:37.000Z","msg":"小麗老母真係賤婦黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef876ff04ca61fca71eef534c5b8e180cbed785","tid":853973,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T05:55:44.000Z","msg":"西九選民選九西"},{"pid":"11a930586fa3a007077ac5d80b1213087c282595","tid":853973,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T05:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061c86803dec22e634ef47295963bf995b79d151","tid":853973,"uid":52122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T06:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小麗老母又唔落啟德宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又想係個度唔見幾多票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地馮檢基都扮下野擺部錄音機播下口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b8cae48d8507d45ecb088ff12d903b636f49ad","tid":853973,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T08:05:43.000Z","msg":"收到消息,九西補選,小麗情況不樂觀,可能會再被DQ,呀基乘機混水摸魚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/850531/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/850531/page/1</a>"}]}